Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eye color, hair color...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even her body appears totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This explains how Angie Sirius\Nhas been able to blind eyes around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lina, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:01:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,First, her camouflage was based on looks,\Nbut now, it's based on position.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To break Parade,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can either destroy the illusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,then find and attack the main body\Nbefore a new illusion is formed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,or locate the main body's coordinates
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and attack using Idea\Nwithout relying on my senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Parade reactivation time is monstrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be too dangerous to move to Idea mode\Nwhile under physical attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jes--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Constant Deceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-Repair Spell... Auto-start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't show her my cards yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Self-Repair Process.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya, you're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to do it in order to capture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to capture me? If you wanted\Nto whisper sweet nothings into my ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've preferred\Na more romantic approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Activate, Dancing Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Two heading for my right arm,\None for my right shoulder, left arm and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,None of them are aimed at a vital spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Corrosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, dismantling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret this, Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've let the target I nearly captured escape.\NI already regret this plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody! Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to end this charade, Angie Sirius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for my rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Major Angelina Sirius,\Ncommander of the Stars magician unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,under the direct command\Nof the USNA Army's Joint Chiefs of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Angie Sirius is the name I use\Nwhen transformed like I was before,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so please continue to call me Lina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know my true identity,\Nthe Stars will have to eliminate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There were plenty of ways to play\Naround the facts if I still had my mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to have wasted the consideration\Nyou were kind enough to show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is a shame, Tatsuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd started to like you\Nquite a bit, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, that was quite the pickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I've got\Nsome questions for you, Lina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's three against one! That's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, shall we have\Na fair contest, one-on-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win, I'll let you go for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, if I win, you'll give\Nhonest answers to my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, would you approve\Nof leaving the duel with Lina to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, why would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lina...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider you a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can never forgive you for\Nattempting to take my brother's life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it wasn't sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to teach you\Na lesson for that sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can beat me, Miyuki?\NThe one granted the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of Sirius?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll let you handle this, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That works for you, Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lose, I'll tell you\Nwhatever you want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can imagine what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.\NWe'll keep our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just going to ask some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only tell you if you beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. We'll keep that promise, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Unworthy though I may be, I, Yakumo Kokonoe,\Nwill preside over this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory will be when one person\Nsurrenders or is incapacitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No killing. It'll leave a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish this before it gets to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,U-U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I had it shown to me before in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It might not be perfect, but I remember how.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The effect is temporary,\Nbut it returns your control, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the delay, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, Lina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not feeling well,\NI'll give you a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll end this with one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it'll take more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worth provoking her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Deceleration Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This magic is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw through it. In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Molecular Divider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dancing Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If my brother hadn't returned\Ncontrol of my magic to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've lost right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she shut down that attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've told her how to protect herself\Nfrom Dancing Blades then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't interfere,\Nbut he did give her advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely can't lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush her with everything I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--Lina!\N--Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--This is it!\N--This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Muspelheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Niflheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, what have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me, Tatsuya. You're the one\Nwho suggested this duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so why did you go\Nand break it up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the "no killing" rule would've been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll say it's my loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At that rate, I would've been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll answer anything you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,However what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My answers will be yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't answer a question\Nthat way, then I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You changed the conditions we agreed on\Nby spoiling our match,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so I hope you don't mind me changing\Na small condition, as well, Tatsuya!
