Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs41\clip(150,44,172,130)\bord0.4\fnOpen Sans Semibold\b0\3c&H000000&\u1\pos(295,90)\t(0,42,\clip(150,44,442,126))}JANUARY 22, 2096
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done for! I don't think\NI can keep doing this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning in the Sirius code name!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You're carrying out\Nyour duty as a member of Sirius wonderfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of commander loses\Nto a high school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you calmed down, Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Silvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone needs to complain sometimes,\Nor they'll explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Silvie, has HQ said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any instructions from HQ,\Nbut I'd like to brief you on several reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,First, regarding the four wounded last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,one was disabled and probably\Nwon't be able to return to duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have to be replaced,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Stars can't afford to dispatch\Nany more personnel to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the General Staff Office\Nwants to send Stardust reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they sending us more chasers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like the strength of Stardust\Nwon't be enough to deal with this situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the investigation into the Strategic-Class\Nmagician who caused Scorched Halloween,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the other team hasn't gotten\Nany noteworthy results yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Other team...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mia's group, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't had\Nthe chance to see Mia recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but she'll be going\Nto First High tomorrow for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going with a delivery\Nof CAD adjustment instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Her afternoon schedule is open,\Nso why not go meet her for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ray...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lovely dress, Tia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You look even more charming than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Those clothes suit you, too, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored you said so, Tia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Tia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,About what you asked me for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the news\Nof a parasite appearing is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause is unknown, but I found\Nsome information that seems to be related.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is under\Na high-level information freeze,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but in November, in Dallas,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,they did an experiment\Nbased on extradimensional theory
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to generate and evaporate\Nmicro black holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Extradimensional theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Even I don't understand the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the details of the experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but the parasites' appearance was observed\Nright after they wrapped that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the experiment and the appearance\Nof the parasites are causally related, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain the black hole experiment\Nwas what called the parasites.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unusual for Tatsuya\Nto summon us on our day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Saegusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jumonji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida and Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Shiba call you guys here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya, why did you\Nsummon us on a Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to inform you regarding\Nthe capture of the parasite we're chasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, I fired a synthetic\Nmolecule device into the parasite...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that transmits a specific pattern\Nof radio wave every three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The transmitter will survive\Nfor three days at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Its radio wave output strength is weak,\Nbut the roadside cameras' surveillance antennae
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that detect and control\Nillegal radio waves are able to receive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Tatsuya. Last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the radio wave frequency and pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You want us to use this\Nto find where the parasite is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why give this to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,About the identity of the parasite\Nwe're chasing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it appears to be a magician\Non the run from the USNA Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, there's more than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, there are at least two deserters,\Nand there could be as many as ten or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten people deserted the Stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Erika, they aren't necessarily\Npart of the Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Stars are a unit\Nof exceptional magicians,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,handpicked from the rest\Nof the USNA Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought military magicians\Nwere strictly controlled in every country,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but has the USNA's military discipline loosened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's probably the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It would mean the parasites' influence\Nwas stronger than military regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Parasites change a human's nature, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If that change is mental\Nas well as physical...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't be strange\Nfor a host's sense of values to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why did the parasites desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know until we catch\Nthe parasites and question them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What do you want us to do anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't intend to tell you what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They hurt a friend of mine,\Nso I don't plan to leave them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, I'm not obsessed\Nwith personally making them regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Clans Council takes responsibility\Nfor dealing with it, I won't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I don't mind if the Chiba Family\Nhunts them on their own, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for having you\Ncome all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:20:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With things being as they are, I thought\Ngiving these to you directly would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hide anything from you, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known from the very beginning\Nthat Lina has been plotting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't want to make any waves\Nin my own life, so I let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a result, I was slow to react.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:21:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'd taken measures right away, there's\Nno guarantee I could've prevented the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm confronted by the fact\Nthat my friend got hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help thinking that\Neven if it's counterproductive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you've become a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki? Where is this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean, you've always been kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Explain it to me\Nin a way I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't forgive the parasites\Nfor harming your friend, Saijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And you also didn't want to get rough\Nwith Lina because you're friends now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it's only been for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you have compassion\Nfor people other than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:22:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your emotions are far more human\Nthan you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Brother...\NYou're hiding your embarrassment.
